pr_title: Fix loop increment and bitcast tensor vals before loading it
pr_body:
As title.

cc @Robertorosmaninho

By the way, you can generate asm and format it with the following command:
```bash
./bin/taco -llvm "a(i) = b(i)" | llc --filetype=asm | python -c 'import sys; print("\n".join(map(lambda x: f"\"{x.rstrip()}\\n\"", sys.stdin)))'
```

Working example is here: https://godbolt.org/z/hWd4Pq4E1
